# Vercel deploys the go aggregator (web/) which imports the shared UI from ui/.
# Everything else in this monorepo is irrelevant to the web build — the 33
# library submodules (their prebuilt API docs already live in web/public/docs),
# the Go doc tools, and build/test artifacts — so keep them out of the upload.
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
web/dist
web/test-results
web/playwright-report
web/coverage
examples
gendocs
genparity
# library submodules (docs are prebuilt into web/public/docs):
algebra
axios
chalk
cheerio
express
fastmcp
gltf
handlebars
jest
jwt
liveview
lodash
lucene
matplotlib
migrate
moment
morgan
nodemailer
numpy
oban
opencv
pandas
passport
pdfkit
prisma
puppeteer
quartz
redis
sharp
sled
socket.io
sqlite
streamlit
